n冇話一定唔食得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e44c4e8e50a2d7be5d71ac058743ea57383c878","tid":1161772,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"做帶氧會快d 喎<br />\n戒甜好緊要"},{"pid":"d67d464111ce2f7e5f9ca2653bcc3e079b71297d","tid":1161772,"uid":190264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4685ecb74ab00f59fad29047cb78e5d67287880","tid":1161772,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3887f699df72dad0f88f903514a985785271215d","tid":1161772,"uid":190264,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"070d94e4f18b722ee93056e54bb9889a90c1e9ff","tid":1161772,"uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"另外纖維係乜？<br />\n正常一般纖維係轉化唔到做能量。<br />\n你係咪想講纖維性較高嘅澱粉？<br />\n如果你係講菜類嘢個種纖維，照你咁死就會變成營養嚴重不足，長久會新陳代謝下降，係極差極差嘅一種減肥方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"亂鳩咁up既佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n脂肪又唔撚計 <br />\n<br />\n認真覆樓主 <br />\n第一<br />\n飲食上面你先google tdee 計算<br />\n計左tdee再跟住黎食 每日食既卡路里tdee-100-300<br />\n個份量食啱左先<br />\n份量啱先再細分啦<br />\n你一日超1000卡路里既話 點分都肥啦係咪先<br />\n第二<br />\n你操成點先 唔係入gym room鳩舉就叫操嫁喎<br />\n你新手期 做多d big3 唔洗舉太重 學識動作先<br />\n好老實你頭3個月都唔會有咩身形明顯改變嫁啦<br />\n因為要學動作，學健身 所以唔好咁急進啦<br />\n比埋片你慢慢研究啦 我健身頭一年都無乜改變嫁<br />\n雖然體重由55kg變左60kg 但...都係好柒<br />\n係依家健第二年先開始越黎越明顯 上到72kg<br />\n唔好比網上d資訊呃鳩你 點樣3個月減肥3個月變肌肉男 唔係咁易嫁 慢慢黎啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JT0-nXAsPdI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJT0-nXAsPdI&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=1ce0a1e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JT0-nXAsPdI</a><a href=\"https://youtu.be/wCO-KlfQJaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwCO-KlfQJaw&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=cd8041c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wCO-KlfQJaw</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:40:16.000Z","msg":"我本身一星期有行5日樓梯機, 每次45分鐘<br />\n另外有做重訓<br />\n文職工<br />\nTDEE 應該係撇除樓梯機定計算埋?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"計埋囉<br />\n因為tdee始終只係大概計算<br />\n唔係完全準確 要慢慢調整<br />\n例如你計左tdee2500 你每日食2400<br />\n但都唔見有瘦 就要2350/2300慢慢調整<br />\n又或者2400 但你見到減肥速度過快<br />\n減好多肌肉 咁就要增加到2500/2550咁<br />\n所以只係參考 要不斷跟你觀察再去調整"},{"pid":"7de384e00b74f0bfda9b9171c51ea8cc6638ca0d","tid":1161772,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14720097bc092ae78443c4d60354b44d48401273","tid":1161772,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"911911284b633a7181af098727d4436845aed8c7","tid":1161772,"uid":25824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"有無TG?<br />\n可以傾傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f14d1d6fc8984c2018f34e8d23b9a6b2dd98d27","tid":1161772,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"樓主你只要增肌就得啦<br />\n你一啲都唔肥<br />\n六呎高有80kg好正常<br />\n增返半年肌再修少少身就好好睇啦"},{"pid":"b35ed610859bf30b3c3ddce163319907fddae558","tid":1161772,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa2ae7d64d3a3e7ff6be8fdf40926452d36f64c","tid":1161772,"uid":101557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01e14044cd8a8cc0a21057c2ae22c1214e4828d6","tid":1161772,"uid":101557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"594166a8891553c3b6ab033c4bdc3040479ec8d9","tid":1161772,"uid":51717,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:55:14.000Z","msg":"閱讀障礙症？<br />\n佢係叫人唔好食過多同要同時食其他唔同嘅營養，你就解讀成唔好食麥皮，你既閱讀障礙極度嚴重喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i